By":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94wn8kp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94wn8kp.jpg&h=cccc11f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ab80c4ef39db28f3edbabca2bfb9da60d4d68c6","tid":1831730,"uid":38651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"2020年仲有人成日提住陳方安生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4408a4643ed5ec9130da7fef2f60414483d79088","tid":1831730,"uid":182061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"認清Gphone係搵到自己嘅position做到嘢囉"},{"pid":"9f4557c19944dc83852aaaadb6338ce97fe62810","tid":1831730,"uid":20563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBw3SOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBw3SOu.jpg&h=4bfcbb05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37ef8d2176dd3f0b972941c31a367d660fd489aa","tid":1831730,"uid":188035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29e99f9f5010eeb968757d0c49e72f1fe08bda5b","tid":1831730,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:07:10.000Z","msg":"...我素來覺得國家把香港定位為科技及創新中心是太抬舉香港了，香港的創新科技基礎、能力及人才各方面均未及深圳。以往，香港在高科技出口方面有優勢，是因為香港從港英時代起，追隨英國享有西方的特別待遇，可以輸入民用軍用高科技產品。<br />\n<br />\n...美國無所不用其極，阻礙中國登上AI一哥的寶座，而香港在中美貿易戰及《法案》的雙重箝制下，未來或者需向美國及其盟友以外的國家（例如德國）輸入科技外，我認為香港另一個可行方向是發展金融科技、虛擬銀行或虛擬貨幣這些相對簡單、不需要採用美國先進半導體或晶片的技術，捨難取易，或有生機，但以香港目前停滯不前的創科環境而言，要突圍也非易事。<br />\n<br />\n...回說1月8日的立法會大會，公民黨郭榮鏗議員振振有詞，說「本人及公民黨支持《香港人權及民主法案》，認為《法案》有助保護香港在《基本法》下應有的人權和法治。」我認為他是顛倒是非。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，香港在多項排名榜表現優良，例如最近菲沙研究所（Fraser Institute）公布的「警察可靠度排名」（Reliability of Police Services），香港排名第六位，比加拿大（第八位）、澳洲（第十位）及英國（第十八位）的排名均要高，美國更只是排名第二十六，遠遠落後。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，<span style=\"color: red;\">市民必須瞪大眼認清楚，正正就是郭榮鏗、楊岳橋、涂謹申、葉建源、陳方安生及黃之鋒等泛民人士，多次赴美，假借保障香港人權自由之名，游說美國國務卿蓬佩奧及其他國會議員通過這條禍港《法案》</span>，要求美國及其盟友制裁香港，真正目的就是箝制中國及香港的發展，將來香港的高新科技無法突圍，這批人「功不可沒」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"岩呀睇清楚幫左香港人幾多野"},{"pid":"6259100a8dfa4421fce92278e54a5a15b31145d2","tid":1831730,"uid":18292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"睇清楚邊啲人先係做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d660eb6976f9ffe1d5a63b7699f7ef651b0144ff","tid":1831730,"uid":85629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6d95e75d68eed61a772707e5ba21fa0e47b35b9","tid":1831730,"uid":82553,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"Solomon: my best friend Regina IP"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"My best friend Regina is still on my list"},{"pid":"664fc88a29efedf43c81d7fb44aacd816f641713","tid":1831730,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話美國有邀請建制派去咩？<br />\n有次鍾國斌都有去架喎<br />\n人地唔buy你就唔buy你架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60cf03fa3af337fce2fda13f60a4d8d9c0d8c4d","tid":1831730,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f4557c19944dc83852aaaadb6338ce97fe62810","tid":1831730,"uid":20563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBw3SOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBw3SOu.jpg&h=4bfcbb05&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9dc5f507997e20170c980793e8fcc8e351f9fa","tid":1831730,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"My best friend"},{"pid":"d4bfa4146e11afd9372c6cc87a8704733bf38e10","tid":1831730,"uid":3358